Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:23.08,EN,,0,0,0,,But I know where to start\N{\c&HC0BB0E&\fn楷体\fs28}但我明白是从何处开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:27.19,EN,,0,0,0,,They tell me I'm too young to understand\N{\c&HC0BB0E&\fn楷体\fs28}人们说我太年轻不需要明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:30.80,EN,,0,0,0,,They say I'm caught up in a dream\N{\c&HC0BB0E&\fn楷体\fs28}他们说我只是沉迷于梦境中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:35.52,EN,,0,0,0,,Well life will pass me by if I don't open up my eyes\N{\c&HC0BB0E&\fn楷体\fs28}如果我不睁开双眼 我的人生将会蹉跎而过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:37.01,EN,,0,0,0,,Well that's fine by me\N{\c&HC0BB0E&\fn楷体\fs28}对此我没意见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:41.56,EN,,0,0,0,,So wake me up when it's all over\N{\c&HC0BB0E&\fn楷体\fs28}所以当一切结束时叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:45.53,EN,,0,0,0,,When I'm wiser and I'm older\N{\c&HC0BB0E&\fn楷体\fs28}当我成熟时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:49.49,EN,,0,0,0,,All this time I was finding myself\N{\c&HC0BB0E&\fn楷体\fs28}这些时光我都在找寻自我
